track_notes:
This is the TrackBack info recorded off my GPS as to the actual route taken. If the River Meig is running high you may find it difficult to cross and I would suggest that you use the ascent as your descent route.

Also, if you have enough time (and fit enough) you could push on and ascend WS-053 and return by crossing the river, but remember if the river is running high you will have a long walk-out.

Enjoy!
